description:
The first 1000 people to use this link will get a 1 month free trial of Skillshare! https://skl.sh/paigelayle12211

QUIZ LINK: https://openpsychometrics.org

some wild questions from the 120 I wanted to point out; 

#35 artistic-scientific
this is rude. this is a hate crime. I AM 100% OF BOTH. ugh. 

#57 sexual-asexual
THIS. is the start of a few questions that bother me. Bc, and please correct me if im wrong... I didn't think the asexuality spectrum included sexual ppl? can one be 97% sexual, and 3% asexual? I dont think that's how that works dude

#58 AUTISTIC-NEUROTYPICAL
MMMMM
MAD
MAD PAIGE
YOU CANNOT BE A PERCENT AUTISTIC OR A PERCENT NEUROTYPICAL. YOU ARE EITHER NEUROTYPICAL. OR NEURODIVERSE.
NT isn't even the opposite of autistic. allistic is. you can be neurodiverse and not be autistic. 
I am 100% autistic... I can't be 50% autistic, 78% autistic, and I am definitely not neurotypical, at any percent, in any capacity.
Fuck this question. this is stupid. 

#70 poisonous-nurturing
??? are those really antonyms????

#79 plastic-wooden
I have full faith that this question is to only determine whether im more like buzz lightyear or woody from toy story. otherwise this makes no sense and makes me feel uneasy. 

#85 straight-queer 
AGAIN!!!!!!! YOU ARE EITHER STRAIGHT. OR YOU ARENT. YOU ARE EITHER QUEER. OR YOU ARENT. Im 0% straight. men may be included in the people I am sexually attracted to but that doesn't make me straight in any capacity, because there are other 'labels' that fit my sexuality, not "straight AND queer at the same time." no. im just fully 100% queer. what the fuck? 

#102 vegan-cannibal
WHAT? Not carnivore- CANNIBAL. HOW MUCH DO YOU EAT HUMANS? AND IF THE ANSWER IS NONE YOU ARE 100% VEGAN. 

#103 French-russian
what if you're neither? or both? I DONT THINK THESE ARE OPPOSITES

#106 genocidal- not genocidal
...

#109 pronatalist-child free
again... not opposites?? I currently am child free, but that doesn't mean im anti baby??

#112 macho-metrosexual
I am neither. and also confused
